<div id="content" class="backgrnd4"><div id="right"><div id="box6"><h2 class="backgrnd12"><span class="text1">Proceedings of the Nineteenth Innovative Applications of Artificial IntelligenceConference</span></h2><div class="content"><p><i>Sponsored by the Association for the Advancement of Artificial Intelligence</i></p><p><b>Edited by William Cheetham and Mehmet Goker</b></p><p>July 22 &ndash; 26 2007, Vancouver, British Columbia, Canada . Published by The AAAI Press, Menlo Park, California. <a href="../../Press/Proceedings/aaai07.php">This proceedings is also available in book and CD format.</a></p><p><b>Please Note:</b> Abstracts are linked to individual titles, and will appear in a separate browser window. Full-text versions of the papers are linked to the abstract text. Access to full text is restricted to AAAI members. PDF file sizes may be large!</p><hr /><h3>Contents</h3><p class="left"><a href="http://www.aaai.org/Library/IAAI/2007/iaai07-000.php" onclick="window.open (this.href, 'child', 'height=500px,width=300px,scrollbars'); return false">Preface, xli</a></p><h3 class="left">IAAI-07 Deployed Application Papers</h3><p class="left"><a href="http://www.aaai.org/Library/IAAI/2007/iaai07-001.php" onclick="window.open (this.href, 'child', 'height=500px,width=300px,scrollbars'); return false">Using AI for e-Government Automatic Assessment of Immigration Application Forms</a><br /><i>Andy Hon Wai Chun</i></p><p class="left"><a href="http://www.aaai.org/Library/IAAI/2007/iaai07-002.php" onclick="window.open (this.href, 'child', 'height=500px,width=300px,scrollbars'); return false">The VITA Financial Services Sales Support Environment</a><br /><i>Alexander Felfernig, Klaus Isak, Kalman Szabo, Peter Zachar</i></p><p class="left"><a href="http://www.aaai.org/Library/IAAI/2007/iaai07-003.php" onclick="window.open (this.href, 'child', 'height=500px,width=300px,scrollbars'); return false">Biomind ArrayGenius and GeneGenius: Web Services Offering Microarray and SNP Data Analysis via Novel Machine Learning Methods</a><br /><i>Ben Goertzel, Cassio Pennachin, Lucio Coelho, Leonardo Shikida, Murilo Queiroz</i></p><p class="left"><a href="http://www.aaai.org/Library/IAAI/2007/iaai07-004.php" onclick="window.open (this.href, 'child', 'height=500px,width=300px,scrollbars'); return false">MasDISPO: A Multiagent Decision Support System for Steel Production and Control</a><br /><i>Sven Jacobi, Esteban Le&oacute;n-Soto, Cristi&aacute;n Madrigal-Mora, Klaus Fischer</i></p><p class="left"><a href="http://www.aaai.org/Library/IAAI/2007/iaai07-005.php" onclick="window.open (this.href, 'child', 'height=500px,width=300px,scrollbars'); return false">Custom DU&reg; &mdash; A Web Based Business User Driven Automated Underwriting System</a><br /><i>Srinivas Krovvidy, Robin Landsman, Steve Opdahl, Nancy Templeton, Sydnor Smalera</i></p><p class="left"><a href="http://www.aaai.org/Library/IAAI/2007/iaai07-006.php" onclick="window.open (this.href, 'child', 'height=500px,width=300px,scrollbars'); return false">Journal-Ranking.com: An Online Interactive Journal Ranking System</a><br /><i>Andrew Lim, Hong Ma, Qi Wen, Zhou Xu, Brenda Cheang, Bernard Tan, Wenbin Zhu</i></p><p class="left"><a href="http://www.aaai.org/Library/IAAI/2007/iaai07-007.php" onclick="window.open (this.href, 'child', 'height=500px,width=300px,scrollbars'); return false">The Virtual Solar-Terrestrial Observatory: A Deployed Semantic Web Application Case Study for Scientific Research</a><br /><i>Deborah McGuinness, Peter Fox, Luca Cinquini, Patrick West, Jose Garcia, James L. Benedict, Don Middleton</i></p><p class="left"><a href="http://www.aaai.org/Library/IAAI/2007/iaai07-008.php" onclick="window.open (this.href, 'child', 'height=500px,width=300px,scrollbars'); return false">Fish Inspection System using a Parallel Neural Network Chip and Image Knowledge Builder Application</a><br /><i>Anne Menendez, Guy Paillet</i></p><p class="left"><a href="http://www.aaai.org/Library/IAAI/2007/iaai07-009.php" onclick="window.open (this.href, 'child', 'height=500px,width=300px,scrollbars'); return false">Enabling Intelligent Content Discovery on the Mobile Internet</a><br /><i>Barry Smyth, Paul Cotter, Stephen Oman</i></p><p class="left"><a href="http://www.aaai.org/Library/IAAI/2007/iaai07-010.php" onclick="window.open (this.href, 'child', 'height=500px,width=300px,scrollbars'); return false">Coordinating Hundreds of Cooperative,  Autonomous Vehicles in Warehouses</a><br /><i>Peter R. Wurman, Raffaello D'Andrea, Mick Mountz</i></p><h3 class="left">IAAI-07 Emerging Applications</h3><p class="left"><a href="http://www.aaai.org/Library/IAAI/2007/iaai07-011.php" onclick="window.open (this.href, 'child', 'height=500px,width=300px,scrollbars'); return false">Real-Time Identification of Operating Room State from Video</a><br /><i>Beenish Bhatia, Tim Oates, Yan Xiao, Peter Hu</i></p><p class="left"><a href="http://www.aaai.org/Library/IAAI/2007/iaai07-012.php" onclick="window.open (this.href, 'child', 'height=500px,width=300px,scrollbars'); return false">Wings for Pegasus: Creating Large-Scale Scientific Applications Using Semantic Representations of Computational Workflows</a><br /><i>Yolanda Gil, Varun Ratnakar, Ewa Deelman, Gaurang Mehta, Jihie Kim</i></p><p class="left"><a href="http://www.aaai.org/Library/IAAI/2007/iaai07-013.php" onclick="window.open (this.href, 'child', 'height=500px,width=300px,scrollbars'); return false">A Multi-Agent Approach to Distributed Rendering Optimization</a><br /><i>Carlos Gonzalez-Morcillo, Gerhard Weiss, Luis Jimenez, David Vallejo</i></p><p class="left"><a href="http://www.aaai.org/Library/IAAI/2007/iaai07-014.php" onclick="window.open (this.href, 'child', 'height=500px,width=300px,scrollbars'); return false">Optimizing Anthrax Outbreak Detection Using Reinforcement Learning</a><br /><i>Masoumeh T. Izadi, David L. Buckeridge</i></p><p class="left"><a href="http://www.aaai.org/Library/IAAI/2007/iaai07-015.php" onclick="window.open (this.href, 'child', 'height=500px,width=300px,scrollbars'); return false">Supporting Feedback and Assessment of Digital Ink Answers to In-Class Exercises</a><br /><i>Kimberle Koile, Kevin Chevalier, Michel Rbeiz, Adam Rogal, David Singer, Jordan Sorensen, Amanda Smith, Kah Seng Tay, Kenneth Wu</i></p><p class="left"><a href="http://www.aaai.org/Library/IAAI/2007/iaai07-016.php" onclick="window.open (this.href, 'child', 'height=500px,width=300px,scrollbars'); return false">Adaptive Timeout Policies for Fast Fine-Grained Power Management</a><br /><i>Branislav Kveton, Prashant Gandhi, Georgios Theocharous, Shie Mannor, Barbara Rosario, Nilesh Shah</i></p><p class="left"><a href="http://www.aaai.org/Library/IAAI/2007/iaai07-017.php" onclick="window.open (this.href, 'child', 'height=500px,width=300px,scrollbars'); return false">RETALIATE: Learning Winning Policies in First-Person Shooter Games</a><br /><i>Megan Smith, Stephen Lee-Urban, H&eacute;ctor Mu&ntilde;oz-Avila</i></p><p class="left"><a href="http://www.aaai.org/Library/IAAI/2007/iaai07-018.php" onclick="window.open (this.href, 'child', 'height=500px,width=300px,scrollbars'); return false">Machine Learning for Automatic Mapping of Planetary Surfaces</a><br /><i>Tomasz F. Stepinski, Soumya Ghosh, Ricardo Vilalta</i></p><p class="left"><a href="http://www.aaai.org/Library/IAAI/2007/iaai07-019.php" onclick="window.open (this.href, 'child', 'height=500px,width=300px,scrollbars'); return false">Optimal Multi-Agent Scheduling with Constraint Programming</a><br /><i>Willem-Jan van Hoeve, Carla P. Gomes, Bart Selman, Michele Lombardi</i></p><p class="left"><a href="http://www.aaai.org/Library/IAAI/2007/iaai07-020.php" onclick="window.open (this.href, 'child', 'height=500px,width=300px,scrollbars'); return false">Stochastic Optimization for Collision Selection in High Energy Physics</a><br /><i>Shimon Whiteson, Daniel Whiteson</i></p><p class="left"><a href="http://www.aaai.org/Library/IAAI/2007/iaai07-021.php" onclick="window.open (this.href, 'child', 'height=500px,width=300px,scrollbars'); return false">An Integrated Development Environment and Architecture for Soar-Based Agents</a><br /><i>Ari Yakir, Gal Kaminka</i></p><p class="left"><a href="http://www.aaai.org/Library/IAAI/2007/iaai07-022	.php" onclick="window.open (this.href, 'child', 'height=500px,width=300px,scrollbars'); return false">Adaptive Traitor Tracing with Bayesian Networks</a><br /><i>Philip Zigoris, Hongxia Jin</i></p></div></div></div><div id="left">
